The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically with light field deblurring using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves 3D scene rendering, which falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of a large-scale dataset and deep learning models suggests that the paper may also belong to the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
